description: Retrieves a list that describes one or more usage report subscriptions.

nested_items.name: UsageReportSubscriptions
nested_items.description: Information about the usage report subscription.

nested_items.name: S3BucketName
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 bucket where generated reports are stored.

nested_items.name: Schedule
nested_items.description: The schedule for generating usage reports.

nested_items.name: LastGeneratedReportDate
nested_items.description: The time when the last usage report was generated.

nested_items.name: SubscriptionErrors
nested_items.description: The errors that were returned if usage reports couldn't be generated.

nested_items.name: ErrorCode
nested_items.description: The error code for the error that is returned when a usage report can't be generated.

nested_items.name: ErrorMessage
nested_items.description: The error message for the error that is returned when a usage report can't be generated.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token to use to retrieve the next page of results for this operation. If there are no more pages, this value is null.
